title: Riot I haven't received my anniversary poro icon.
body: I got the riot kayle skin but not the icon.

replies.body: Gifts are still being distributed and not everyone has received them all just yet.  Stay up to date on our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight and it will come in time!
The gifts are still being handed out, and the final date to receive them has been moved to the 30th, as per the banner on the [support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us).
